</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Abbt des Cloſters cʒu Salfelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l3">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu </del> ſant Benedicten ordens </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_54_r1l5"><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Erwirdikeit voꝛmals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l6"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von frawn Elſpeten der <expan>Cam<ex>m</ex>ermeiſterin</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l7"><expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> kinde wegen vnd irs hofs cʒum dörffleins etc Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l8">dÿ <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>Burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ~ Jre kindeꝛ <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l9">vvie ſich ewr 
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr </del> Erwırdıkeit gen Jn darynne gar günſtiklıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l10">
<del rend="strikethrough">ge </del> bevveiſet hab . des vvir euch mit fleiſʒ dancken . Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l11">euch fürbaʒ <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> aber darynne günſtiklıch wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l12"> <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſen . Alſo . 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Er ew ſie ewr genyſſen </del> . daʒ ſıe dabey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l13"><expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darcʒu ſıe <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> reht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd daʒ Jn auch des ein ſlewnig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_54_r1l14">ende werde vnd ewr darynne genyſſen . Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_54" id="26r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, abbt des closters czu Salfelt sant
                        Benedicten ordens</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erwirdikeit vormals
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von frawn Elspeten der
                            <expan>Cam<ex>m</ex>ermeisterin</expan> und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        kinde wegen und irs hofs czum Dörffleins etc., also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns dy <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
                        unser <expan>burgerin<ex>n</ex></expan> und ire kinder
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbraht, wie sich ewr erwirdikeit
                        gen in darynne gar günstiklich beweiset hab, des wir euch mit fleisz
                        dancken. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir euch fürbaz
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> aber darynne günstiklich wöllet
                                <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lassen, also daz sie dabey
                                <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darczu sie
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> reht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und daz
                        in auch des ein slewnig ende werde und ewr darynne genyssen. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
